SELECT
    INITCAP(x5.display_name) AS guest_display_name,
    LOWER(x5.email) AS guest_email,
    x1.ref_no AS id,
    x1.status,
    x2.registration_no,
    x2.url,
    x4.NAME AS brand,
    x3.NAME AS model,
    TO_CHAR(x1.request_start_at + INTERVAL '8 hours', 'Day, dd Month') AS request_start_date,
    TO_CHAR(x1.request_start_at + INTERVAL '8 hours', 'hh12:miAM') AS request_start_time,
    TO_CHAR(x1.request_end_at + INTERVAL '8 hours', 'Day, dd Month') AS request_end_date,
    TO_CHAR(x1.request_end_at + INTERVAL '8 hours', 'hh12:miAM') AS request_end_time,
    d1.rental,
    d2.insurance,
    COALESCE(d3.pickup, 0) AS pickup,
    COALESCE(d4.dropoff, 0) AS dropoff,
    COALESCE(d5.rental_ext, 0) AS rental_ext,
    COALESCE(d6.insurance_ext, 0) AS insurance_ext,
    COALESCE(x6.discount_amount, 0) AS discount,
    d1.rental + d2.insurance + COALESCE(d3.pickup, 0) + COALESCE(d4.dropoff, 0) + COALESCE(d5.rental_ext, 0) + COALESCE(d6.insurance_ext, 0) AS gross_amount,
    d1.rental + d2.insurance + COALESCE(d3.pickup, 0) + COALESCE(d4.dropoff, 0) + COALESCE(d5.rental_ext, 0) + COALESCE(d6.insurance_ext, 0) - COALESCE(x6.discount_amount, 0) AS net_amount
FROM bookings x1
LEFT JOIN listings x2 ON x1.listing_id = x2.id
LEFT JOIN models x3 ON x2.model_id = x3.id
LEFT JOIN brands x4 ON x3.brand_id = x4.id
LEFT JOIN users x5 ON x1.user_id = x5.id
LEFT JOIN booking_common_promos x6 ON x1.id = x6.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
    (
      SELECT booking_id, amount AS rental
      FROM booking_lines
      WHERE slug = 'rental-fee'
    ) d1 ON x1.id = d1.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
    (
      SELECT booking_id, amount AS insurance
      FROM booking_lines
      WHERE NAME IN ('SCDW', 'Lite', 'Standard', 'Premium')
    ) d2 ON x1.id = d2.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
    (
      SELECT booking_id, amount AS pickup
      FROM booking_lines
      WHERE slug = 'car-pick-up-fee'
    ) d3 ON x1.id = d3.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
    (
      SELECT booking_id, amount AS dropoff
      FROM booking_lines
      WHERE slug = 'car-drop-off-fee'
    ) d4 ON x1.id = d4.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
    (
      SELECT t2.booking_id, t2.amount AS rental_ext
      FROM booking_extension t1
      LEFT JOIN booking_lines t2 ON t1.booking_id = t2.booking_id AND t1.id = t2.entity_id
      WHERE t1.currency = 'myr' AND t1.status = 'accepted' AND t2.slug = 'extension'
    ) d5 ON x1.id = d5.booking_id
LEFT JOIN
    (
      SELECT t2.booking_id, t2.amount AS insurance_ext
      FROM booking_extension t1
      LEFT JOIN booking_lines t2 ON t1.booking_id = t2.booking_id AND t1.id = t2.entity_id
      WHERE t1.currency = 'myr' AND t1.status = 'accepted' AND t2.slug LIKE 'scdw-extension-%'
    ) d6 ON x1.id = d6.booking_id
WHERE
    x1.request_end_at >= NOW() - INTERVAL '2 hours'
    AND x1.currency = 'myr'
    AND x1.status = 'completed'
ORDER BY
    x1.request_end_at DESC;
